http://localhost:8080/sys/dept/save.json?name=行政部&seq=3&remark=行政部门
http://localhost:8080/sys/dept/save.json?name=财务一组&seq=1&remark=财务部门
http://localhost:8080/sys/dept/save.json?name=财务二组&seq=2&remark=财务部门

http://http://localhost:8080/sys/dept/tree.json

http://localhost:8080/sys/dept/update.json?id=2&name=后端开发&seq=1&parentId=1&remark=后端项目组

http://localhost:8080/sys/dept/update.json?id=3&name=前端开发&seq=2&parentId=1&remark=前端项目组

